snippet.title: [BEENA] ハローキティのひらがな・カタカナ・おなまえかいてみよう！ | Hello Kitty no Hiragana Katakana o-Namae Kaitemiyou!
snippet.description:
Somehow, in spite of my lack of free time, I've managed another Beena game recording.

This Hello Kitty game has Hiragana/Katakana lessons, and minigames designed to teach youngsters to memorize the names of objects.

... Didn't I hear that "failure" jingle in another Beena game?

[Joke about Sonic x Hello Kitty and/or Sonic x Hooters goes here]
